<P><PB N="58" REF="57">
<Q>&startq;Over and above which, the Merchants &s;ell about a Hundred Tons. I hope the Con&s;umption I meet &endq;with as I go, will give Content; and am,</Q></P>
<CLOSER><SALUTE>SIR,</SALUTE>
<SIGNED><HI>Your</HI>, &amp;c Robt. Ibbot&s;on</SIGNED></CLOSER>
</LETTER>
